---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service - Arclet Copier" lang="en">
  <Header lang="en" />

  <main class="pt-24 pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-soft-lg p-8 md:p-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-serif font-semibold text-secondary-900 mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>

        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <p class="text-secondary-600 mb-8">Last updated: December 3, 2025</p>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary-900 mb-4">The Basics</h2>
            <p class="text-secondary-700">
              Using Arclet Copier means you agree to these terms. Simple as that.
            </p>
            <p class="text-secondary-700 mt-4">
              If something here doesn't work for you, no hard feelings. Just don't use the extension.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary-900 mb-4">Free and Open</h2>
            <p class="text-secondary-700 mb-4">
              Arclet Copier is open source under GPL-3.0. That means you can:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-secondary-700 space-y-2">
              <li>Use it for free, forever</li>
              <li>Read and modify the source code</li>
              <li>Share it with others</li>
              <li>Use it for work or personal projects</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-secondary-700 mt-4">
              <strong>One rule:</strong> If you change the code and share it, make your changes open source too. That's how good things spread.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary-900 mb-4">Be Respectful</h2>
            <p class="text-secondary-700 mb-4">Don't use this extension to:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-secondary-700 space-y-2">
              <li>Break laws or hurt people</li>
              <li>Steal or misuse others' work</li>
              <li>Spread harmful stuff</li>
              <li>Mess with how the extension works</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-secondary-700 mt-4">
              Common sense, really. Treat others how you'd want to be treated.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary-900 mb-4">Your Responsibility</h2>
            <p class="text-secondary-700 mb-4">When you copy content with Arclet Copier:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-secondary-700 space-y-2">
              <li>Make sure you have the right to use what you copy</li>
              <li>Respect copyright and other people's rights</li>
              <li>Take ownership of how you use the tool</li>
              <li>Keep your device and data secure</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-secondary-700 mt-4">
              We built a tool. What you do with it is on you.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary-900 mb-4">
              No Promises
            </h2>
            <p class="text-secondary-700 mb-4">
              Arclet Copier comes "as is." We can't promise:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-secondary-700 space-y-2">
              <li>It'll work perfectly for your needs</li>
              <li>It'll never have bugs</li>
              <li>It'll always be available</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-secondary-700 mt-4">
              We work hard to make it good. But we're human. Sometimes things break.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary-900 mb-4">
              Not Liable
            </h2>
            <p class="text-secondary-700">
              We're not responsible if something goes wrong—data loss, missed work, anything else. Use this extension at your own risk.
            </p>
            <p class="text-secondary-700 mt-4">
              This isn't personal. It's just how free tools work.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary-900 mb-4">
              Respect Copyright
            </h2>
            <p class="text-secondary-700">
              Our code is open source under GPL-3.0. When you copy web content, respect the original creators' rights.
            </p>
            <p class="text-secondary-700 mt-4">
              Good tools enable good work. Use them wisely.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary-900 mb-4">If Terms Change</h2>
            <p class="text-secondary-700">
              We'll update this page when terms change. We won't notify you separately—check back here if you're curious.
            </p>
            <p class="text-secondary-700 mt-4">
              Keep using the extension, and you're agreeing to the new terms. We won't change things without good reason.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary-900 mb-4">You Can Leave Anytime</h2>
            <p class="text-secondary-700">
              Don't like it? Uninstall it. No questions asked.
            </p>
            <p class="text-secondary-700 mt-4">
              If you violate these terms, we might ask you to stop using it. Fair's fair.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary-900 mb-4">Questions?</h2>
            <p class="text-secondary-700 mb-4">
              Reach out via email or Discord. We're here to help.
            </p>
            <p class="text-secondary-700">
              Email:
              <a
                href="mailto:hi@coryso.com"
                class="text-primary-600 underline hover:text-primary-700"
              >
                hi@coryso.com
              </a>
            </p>
            <p class="text-secondary-700 mt-2">
              Discord:
              <a
                href="https://discord.gg/NpRnQ5zp5q"
                class="text-primary-600 underline hover:text-primary-700"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
              >
                Join our community
              </a>
            </p>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer lang="en" />
</Layout>
